{"tid":1927682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怎確定中国大陸疫情真趨緩？ 台灣網友提出「判斷關鍵」","createTime":"2020-03-16T02:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T02:30:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"235be62f206304c122111040dc4829cdd71ab7cb","tid":1927682,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T02:26:35.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（ COVID-19 ）疫情延燒，不僅亞洲國家，歐洲各國也大規模淪陷，相較之下中國大陸疫情已經看似趨緩許多。對此，就有網友在 PTT 八卦版好奇詢問，如何確定中國大陸疫情是真的穩定了？貼文立刻引發熱議，網友們意見一面倒，紛紛狂喊「一關鍵」。<br />\n<br />\n原 PO 表示，中國大陸在疫情爆發後，一度將疫情擴散元凶推給美國，並稱「數據發布全由中國大陸政府說了算，其本質根本缺乏公正性」，認為實際上中國大陸境內感染數，官方依舊無法確定，尤其是聽到武漢解除封城，不禁疑惑中國大陸何以如此肯定疫情不會復發，畢竟是人口稠密的國家，直問「哪來的信心？有什麼方法肯定中國大陸疫情真的穩定下來？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3U4WUwttIxTHTBrnW2BweQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/22edde935a9b78eabb998402f0a064ad\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3U4WUwttIxTHTBrnW2BweQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F22edde935a9b78eabb998402f0a064ad&h=24ae34bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自 PTT ）<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，隨即引發熱烈討論，網友們意見一面倒向一關鍵「問北韓」、「看北韓什麼時候開放邊境」、「北韓跟俄羅斯何時開放，就表示真的好轉了」、「要看北韓，別上當」、「很簡單，如果俄羅斯和北韓沒封邊界那大概就真的穩了」、「北韓邊境解禁」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，也有網友表示「我相信有減緩， 0 人我就不相信了」、「因為他們再不開工，會比疫情爆發更慘」、「等中國大陸小學生開學」、「黃安回去的時候」、「可能人數真的有壓下來」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%80%8E%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E7%9C%9F%E8%B6%A8%E7%B7%A9-%E7%9C%BE%E6%9B%9D-%E5%88%A4%E6%96%B7%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5-%E5%88%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%95%B6-011258937.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2580%258E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%259C%259F%25E8%25B6%25A8%25E7%25B7%25A9-%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%259B%259D-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%2596%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%258D%25B5-%25E5%2588%25A5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2595%25B6-011258937.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=dcd02c2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%80%8E%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E7%9C%9F%E8%B6%A8%E7%B7%A9-%E7%9C%BE%E6%9B%9D-%E5%88%A4%E6%96%B7%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5-%E5%88%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%95%B6-011258937.html</a>"},{"pid":"19458c5517e8ce4044053589e1f18185e88030e9","tid":1927682,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"唔開工 100%餓死<br />\n開左 最多20%死亡率"},{"pid":"4b1ed75a6aa6cc013f721cc364a3741aa3a9b49c","tid":1927682,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T02:29:44.000Z","msg":"台灣no.1"},{"pid":"d596f4d38ef9c32b55c2b4849b4389a350a16f95","tid":1927682,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"我只信台灣"}]}